        <item>
            <title>警方再向市民发短讯，防骗视伏 App 升级加入可疑来电警示</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/scameter-new-app-announcement-from-hkpf/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=scameter-new-app-announcement-from-hkpf</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/scameter-new-app-announcement-from-hkpf/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 11:00:56 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[防骗视伏器]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1225773</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日香港警察发送短讯，表示已推出升级版「防骗视伏 App」，加入了新功能如可疑来电话警示、可疑网站侦测，以及公众诈骗举报平台。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1225774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/418951742_3779183852-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/418951742_3779183852-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/418951742_3779183852-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p>全新升级版「防骗视伏 App」目前已经可在 App Store、Google Play 及 Huawei AppGallery 下载或更新。警方呼吁市民早日下载，以减低受骗风险。</p><p>上月警方发言人表示，升级程式后市民不用额外设定任何手续，即可接收防骗资讯。与以往相比，相信对市民而言更加方便，因此警方相信升级后应用程式反诈骗成效将更加显著。发言人又强调，警方致力遵守个人资料私隐条例，升级应用程式后亦不会储存市民来电和网页浏览纪录。发言人另外指，新增的「公众举报平台」收集用户电话号码仅不会用作其他用途，仅以发出验证短讯之用。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/26/scameter-new-app-auto-distinguish-scam-call-and-web/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">防骗视伏 APP 升级版可识别诈骗来电及网站，警方强调：不会储存纪录</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/scameter-new-app-announcement-from-hkpf/fun-tech/">警方再向市民发短讯，防骗视伏 App 升级加入可疑来电警示</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/scameter-new-app-announcement-from-hkpf/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
